Core Capabilities
- Multi-threaded rendering hooks for custom heads-up displays (HUD) and vector projection arrays.
- Real-time modification tracking matrices managing active variables (Reach values, click intervals) on-the-fly.
- Direct integration via standard JVM process attach protocols, native memory boundaries, and execution loops.
- Smart configuration pattern templates and macro support for fast layout hot-reloads.
- Optimized low-overhead memory mapping engineered to run parallel to intensive game loops.

